PrecisOrder authorizing the trip to the MIDDLE EAST (Egypt, Kuwait, Lebanon and Saudi Arabia) and to WARSAW, Poland, made by Mr. MAC HARB, M.P., from April 22 to May 7, 1994, in order to attend or participate in a number of trade exhibitions and to represent the Minister for International Trade at the third East-West Conference of Ministers of Economy, Industry and Trade.
